      "text": "Triplet loss reaches near-zero in epoch 2 because the fixed margin (0.3) is already exceeded by random sentence pairs.\nInfoNCE has no fixed margin — it always provides gradient signal as long as the model hasn't perfectly ranked all pairs.",
